ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of SARA HRADECKY of Victoria, British Columbia, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Caroline Lavoie, whose term has expired.
